Title
Added Corners
Description
Enter the digits 1 through 8 (one digit of each value) into 
the      circles and squares at right so that sum of the digits 
in any    two circles appears in the square that lies 
between them.      Equations below assume that the 
figures are assigned letters    "a" though "h" as shown.  
Adapted from "The Giant Book of  Mensa Mind Challenges", 
 Stirling Publications, 2003 
Numbers
1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8
Equations
a+c=b
c+e=d
e+g=f
g+a=h
